    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "summary": "In this prophetic tradition, the Prophet Muhammad (PBUH) draws a remarkable comparison between Imam Ali (AS) and three of the greatest prophets in Islamic tradition. He declares that whoever wants to see Adam's noble creation, Noah's wisdom, and Ibrahim's forbearance, should look at Ali. This hadith establishes the extraordinary status of Ali as embodying the finest qualities of these prophets.",
        "key_terms": {
